---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us - KPPF.EU" description="Learn about KPPF - premium paint protection film manufacturer serving the European market.">
  <section class="py-20 bg-kppf-black">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-head mb-6">About <span class="text-kppf-green">KPPF</span></h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-kppf-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Created by professionals, for professionals. Premium paint protection film now available across Europe.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-head mb-6 text-kppf-green">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-kppf-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            <p>KPPF was born from a simple idea: detailing professionals deserve materials that match their skill level. Too many films on the market compromise on quality, forcing masters to work around material limitations.</p>
            <p>We partnered with leading polyurethane film manufacturers to develop a product line that meets the highest standards — self-healing without heat, chemical resistance, anti-yellowing technology, and a deep gloss finish.</p>
            <p>Now, we're bringing this commitment to quality to the European market, with our headquarters in Stockholm, Sweden.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-kppf-gray-700 to-kppf-gray-800 rounded-2xl h-80 flex items-center justify-center border border-kppf-gray-700/50">
          <span class="text-kppf-gray-500">Company Photo</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Values -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20">
        {[
          { icon: "🏆", title: "Quality First", desc: "Every roll undergoes rigorous quality control. We never compromise on materials or manufacturing standards." },
          { icon: "🤝", title: "Professional Partnership", desc: "We work directly with detailing studios, providing training, support, and materials for exceptional results." },
          { icon: "🌍", title: "European Commitment", desc: "Local presence, fast delivery, and dedicated support. We're here to serve the growing PPF market across Europe." },
        ].map((v) => (
          <div class="bg-kppf-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-kppf-gray-700/50 hover:border-kppf-green/30 transition-all text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">{v.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">{v.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-kppf-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">{v.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Why KPPF -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-20">
        {[
          { title: "Self-Healing Technology", desc: "Minor scratches disappear naturally without heat treatment — just sunlight or warm water." },
          { title: "Up to 7 Years Durability", desc: "Long-lasting protection that maintains clarity and performance year after year." },
          { title: "Anti-Yellowing Formula", desc: "Advanced UV-resistant coating prevents yellowing, keeping your vehicle looking fresh." },
          { title: "Easy Installation", desc: "Highly elastic film that forgives positioning errors and stretches to conform to any body shape." },
        ].map((f) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-kppf-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-kppf-gray-700/30">
            <div class="text-kppf-green text-xl flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✓</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">{f.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-kppf-gray-400 text-sm">{f.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-kppf-green">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-head text-kppf-black mb-4">Ready to Partner with KPPF?</h2>
      <p class="text-kppf-black/70 text-lg mb-8">Get in touch to discuss pricing, distribution, or place your first order.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-kppf-black hover:bg-kppf-black-500 text-kppf-green font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
